==概述==
Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh 版是Mac平台首款支持[[QuickTime|QuickTime]]视频的office套件，是微软为了抢占Mac机用户，首次为苹果机提供的Mac Office版本<ref>{{cite news|author=芬达|title=V3评微软史上十大重磅发布|url=http://news.newhua.com/news1/news/2009/1026/09102695379197E6AA3HDK39095KA61JC2A50I9GA5I541KBG5H16I0.html|accessdate=2013-11-28|newspaper=华军资讯|date=2009-10-26|language=zh-cn|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414052031/http://news.newhua.com/news1/news/2009/1026/09102695379197E6AA3HDK39095KA61JC2A50I9GA5I541KBG5H16I0.html|archivedate=2010-04-14}}</ref>。微软Office98中的应用程序如下：<!--It included drag–and-drop installation, self-repairing applications and Quick Thesaurus before such features were available in a version of Office for Windows. It also was the first version to support QuickTime movie. The applications in Microsoft Office 98 were:-->
*[[Microsoft_PowerPoint|Microsoft PowerPoint]] 98
*[[Microsoft_Word|Microsoft Word]] 98
*[[Microsoft_Excel|Microsoft Excel]] 98
*[[Outlook_Express|Outlook Express]] 4.0
*[[Internet_Explorer_for_Mac#Internet_Explorer_version_4.0_for_Macintosh|Internet Explorer]] 4.0
微软还十分罕见的另外发布了一个名为“Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Gold Edition”的特别版。这个版本除了包含普通版本所有的应用套件外，还包含[[Microsoft_FrontPage|Microsoft FrontPage]]的Macintosh1.0版、Microsoft Bookshelf 98参考软件和Microsoft Encarta98 Macintosh豪华版。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Microsoft-Office-Macintosh-Edition-Gold/dp/B0014JDKPS/ref=pd_sim_sbs_sw_1|title=Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Edition Gold: Software|accessdate=2013-11-28|work=Amazon.com|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018123651/https://www.amazon.com/Microsoft-Office-Macintosh-Edition-Gold/dp/B0014JDKPS/ref=pd_sim_sbs_sw_1|dead-url=no}}</ref>
